tion of a recent reduction of soviet rail freight rates for peiping's benefit known charges paid by peiping on imports by rail from european countries have heretofore corresponded with those published in the 1950 schedule of internal soviet freight rates according to this schedule the charges on a shipment of fertilizer would be 280 rubles a ton", "unred_source_page": 3}
